  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_weak</Cell><Cell>The weakest will do.</Cell><Cell>最弱的就行。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_provider_weak</Cell><Cell>Alright, 50 groschen a head. How many do you need?</Cell><Cell>好的，每人50格罗申。你需要几个？</Cell></Row>
  
  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_medium</Cell><Cell>Some decent lads.</Cell><Cell>一些不错的伙子。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_provider_medium</Cell><Cell>Alright, 100 groschen a head. How many do you need?</Cell><Cell>好的，每人100格罗申。你需要几个？</Cell></Row>
  
