  <Row><Cell>merc_henry_equip_ska</Cell><Cell>Wear the colors of Skalitz and Leipa.</Cell><Cell>穿上斯卡里茨和莱帕的颜色。</Cell></Row>
  <Row><Cell>merc_test_equip_ska</Cell><Cell>For Sir Radzig!</Cell><Cell>为了拉德季大人！</Cell></Row>

